==French==
===Etymology===
From Gallo-Latin ''*wespa'', a conflation of Latin [[vespa]] with a Germanic word (cf. Old High German [[wafsa]]).

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/gɛp/}}

===Noun===
'''guêpe''' ''f''
# [[wasp]]

===Derived terms===
*[[guêpier]] ‘bee-eater’
*[[guêpière]] ‘basque’

